sh the normal ending was more of an ending and the extra ending and content maybe would be better incorporated into a single gameplay with perhaps different paths or whatever.ill update again if i get around to using the clear save and doing the extra content with a different ending, not sure if its just a quick refight or if its going to provide enough content to properly conclude the story in any satisfying manner.  Im almost sort of♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥off how it ended tbh.  Still had a lot of fun with it for the price and has been one of the better oldschool jrpgs ive played in a while."
