ike the ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ here. And again since there are very few side quests there few people to meet- This is just a bonus - The romance sucks, not because Asdivine hearts is a harem and well, who doesn't like harems? but because there's no depth in the relationship of the people involved plus the concept is cliche"
